# NetGuard Pro README

## Overview

**NetGuard Pro** is an all-in-one enterprise network management platform developed by NetGuard Solutions. It helps organisations monitor network traffic, improve performance, detect security threats, and manage infrastructure from a single dashboard.

Designed for both small teams and large enterprises, NetGuard Pro combines:

* Real-time network monitoring
* Traffic optimization
* Built-in security tools
* Cloud integration
* Automation and alerting

