# Troubleshooting

## Installation Issues

### Problem

Installer fails to launch.

### Solution

* Verify operating system compatibility
* Ensure sufficient disk space
* Run installer with administrator permissions

---

## High Resource Usage

### Problem

Slow system performance after deployment.

### Solution

* Upgrade RAM to 16 GB recommended minimum
* Use SSD storage for better performance
* Reduce unnecessary background services

---

## Devices Not Detected

### Problem

Connected devices are missing from the dashboard.

### Solution

* Check network adapter configuration
* Verify firewall permissions
* Restart the network scan from the dashboard

---

## Alert Notifications Not Working

### Problem

Slack or PagerDuty alerts are not received.

### Solution

* Verify integration API credentials
* Check internet connectivity
* Test alert configuration settings

